end.rcode-->

  <p>Errors, messages and warnings can be put into <code>div</code>'s
  with different <code>class</code>es:</p>

<!--begin.rcode
sqrt(-1)  # warning
message('knitr says hello to HTML!')
1+'a'  # mission impossible
end.rcode-->

